&lt;h1 id=&#34;the-why-and-what-of-nlp&#34;&gt;The Why and What of NLP&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This session is an introduction session to NLP. We will first motivate the uses and potential uses of NLP. We then will introduce some key linguistics concept for NLP. Finally, we will describe NLP in three standart pipelines.&lt;/p&gt;

