&lt;h1 id=&#34;representing-text-into-vectors&#34;&gt;Representing text into vectors&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This course will cover representation learning techniques for Natural Language Processing with a specific focus on word representation. We start with feature based approaches. We then study continuous approaches based using co-occurence matrices. We end with word embedding techniques such as word2vec.&lt;/p&gt;

