&lt;h1 id=&#34;task-specific-modelling-of-text&#34;&gt;Task-specific Modelling of Text&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This course will cover a standart task-specific NLP pipeline. We will study preprocessing steps such as encoding and tokenization. We will then focus on sequence labelling illustrated by POS (Part-of-Speech) tagging and Name-Entity Recognition (NER). Finally, we will present standart evaluation metrics for classification tasks.&lt;/p&gt;

